<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - NUPAC</title>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

    <style>
        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-100">

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
        
        <div class="bg-white shadow-lg rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12">

            <div class="text-center mb-10">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800">
                    Privacy Policy
                </h1>

                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">
                    NUPAC - National University of Pakistan Affiliated Colleges
                </p>

                <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mt-2">
                    Last Updated: June 28, 2026
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-8 text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">
                        Introduction
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        Welcome to NUPAC (National University of Pakistan Affiliated Colleges).
                        Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how
                        information is handled when you use our mobile application.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">
                        Information We Collect
                    </h2>

                    <p class="mb-4">
                        NUPAC does not collect, store, process, or share any personal
                        information from users.
                    </p>

                    <p class="mb-3">
                        Specifically, we do not collect:
                    </p>

                    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
                        <li>Names</li>
                        <li>Email Addresses</li>
                        <li>Phone Numbers</li>
                        <li>Student IDs</li>
                        <li>Location Data</li>
                        <li>Contacts</li>
                        <li>Photos or Media Files</li>
                        <li>Financial Information</li>
                        <li>Device Identifiers</li>
                        <li>Usage Analytics</li>
                        <li>Any Personally Identifiable Information (PII)</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">
                        Data Storage
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        NUPAC does not require user registration and does not store any
                        personal information on servers, databases, or third-party
                        platforms.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">
                        Third-Party Services
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        NUPAC does not use advertising networks, analytics services,
                        tracking technologies, or any third-party systems that collect
                        user information.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">
                        Children's Privacy
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        NUPAC does not knowingly collect personal information from anyone,
                        including children under the age of 13.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">
                        Data Security
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        Since NUPAC does not collect or store user information,
                        there is no personal data maintained on our systems.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">
                        Changes to This Privacy Policy
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
                        Any changes will be reflected on this page by updating
                        the "Last Updated" date above.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-3">
                        Contact Us
                    </h2>

                    <p>
                        If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy,
                        please contact us:
                    </p>

                    <div class="mt-4 bg-slate-50 border rounded-xl p-4">
                        <p><strong>NUPAC Team</strong></p>
                        <p>Email: support@nupac.pk</p>
                    </div>
                </section>

            </div>

            <div class="border-t mt-10 pt-6 text-center text-sm text-slate-500">
                By using NUPAC, you acknowledge that you have read and understood
                this Privacy Policy.
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
